translated: Eklund, Hans Johan Henrik Teodor, city secretary, Norrköping, b. February 7th, 1899 in Stockholm to merchant Allan E. and Hedvig Johansson. Married on June 26th to Sigrid Gartz. Children: Birgitta (born) 1927, Hans 1929, Marianne 1934, Louise 1947. Graduated high school in 1916 and received a law degree in 1920. Second notary in Sevede and Tunaläns district court from 1921-1922, first notary there in 1922, first notary in North and South Tjust district court from 1926-1927. City council member in Västervik from 1922-1935, city secretary in Norrköping since 1935.
